@CowboysStats Only one QB has been more vindicated  by the #nflverse than Dak Prescott.

That QB would be Antonio Ramiro (Tony) Romo.

Inspired by the now famous @tejfbanalytics interception risk chart, I decided to extend the plot to also include fumbles.

Baker, Jameis and Allen seem to take calculated risks. Burrow on the other hand...
